Class Employee

com.android.Employee
public final class Employee
extends Object
this is an immutable class Employee and using an nested inner static class EmployeeBuilder to create Employee's with setters for each variable and a builder to return this object To see video tutorial for this section of code Video tutorial For all 177 videos, which cover all the topics in this course go to Complete Course Video Tutorial
